<Body>
	<Title>陕西西汉高速30多辆车连环相撞4死16伤</Title>
	<ReportTime type="absTime">2007-10-11</ReportTime>
<Content>
<Paragraph>
<Sentence>	
        <Event eid="e1" type="thoughtevent"><Participant sid="s1">中新社</Participant><Location lid="l1">西安</Location><Time tid="t1" type="relTime">十月十日</Time><Denoter did="d1" type="statement">电</Denoter></Event> (记者 冽玮)
</Sentence>
    <Sentence><Event eid="e2" type="thoughtevent"><Participant type="agent" sid="s2">记者</Participant>从<Participant type="recipient" oid="o2">陕西有关部门</Participant>
    <Denoter type="perception" did="d2">获悉</Denoter></Event>，
    <Event eid="e3">刚刚开通不久的<Location lid="l3">西(安)至汉(中)高速公路</Location><Time type="relTime" tid="t3">八日</Time>发生重大<Denoter type="emergency" did="d3">交通事故</Denoter></Event>，
    <Event eid="e4"><Object sid="s4">三十多辆车</Object>连环<Denoter type="action" did="d4">相撞</Denoter></Event>，目前共导致<Event eid="e5"><Participant sid="s5">四人</Participant><Denoter type="stateChange" did="d5">死亡</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e6"><Participant sid="s6">十六人</Participant><Denoter type="stateChange" did="d6">受伤</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence>
    <Sentence><Event eid="e7"><Object sid="s7">西汉高速公路</Object>单幅<Denoter type="stateChange" did="d7">中断</Denoter>已<Time type="timeInterval" tid="t7">超过三十个小时</Time></Event></Sentence>。</Paragraph>  
　　<Paragraph><Sentence>据了解，<Event eid="e8"><Time type="absTime" tid="t8">二00二年九月</Time><Denoter type="operation" did="d8">开工</Denoter>的<Object sid="s8">西(安)汉(中)高速公路</Object></Event>，穿越秦岭和巴山，连接关中平原和汉中平原，通往成都平原，是国家高速公路北京―昆明线路在陕西境内的重要组成部分。</Sentence>
<Sentence>公路全长两百五十五公里，共有桥梁五百四十座，隧道一百三十六座，
于<Event eid="e9"><Time type="relTime" tid="t9">今年九月三十日</Time>正式<Denoter type="stateChange" did="d9">通车</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph> 
　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e10"><Time type="relTime" tid="t10">十月八日</Time>，<Object sid="s10">西汉高速汉中到西安方向涝峪段</Object>发生多起<Denoter type="emergency" did="d10">交通事故</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e11">造成<Object sid="s11">三十多辆车</Object>不同程度<Denoter type="action" did="d11">相撞</Denoter></Event>，并导致<Event eid="e12"><Participant sid="s12">四人</Participant><Denoter type="stateChange" did="d12">死亡</Denoter></Event>，
<Event eid="e13"><Participant sid="s13">十六人</Participant><Denoter type="stateChange" did="d13">受伤</Denoter></Event>，
<Event eid="e14"><Object sid="s14">西汉高速公路汉中到西安方向路段</Object>被迫<Denoter type="stateChange" did="d14">中断</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence>
<Sentence>有<Event eid="e15"><Participant sid="s14">知情者</Participant><Denoter type="statement" did="d14">透露</Denoter></Event>，由于
<Event eid="e16"><Time type="relTime" tid="t16">十月八日</Time>系<Object sid="s16">西汉高速公路</Object>第一天对<Object oid="o16">大货车</Object><Denoter type="stateChange" did="d16">放行</Denoter></Event>，
<Event eid="e17"><Object sid="s17">大批大货车</Object>
<Denoter type="action" did="d17">进入</Denoter>
<Object did="d17">高速路</Object></Event>。</Sentence>
<Sentence><Event eid="e18"><Participant sid="s18">一些司机</Participant><Denoter type="operation" did="d18">驾车</Denoter></Event>车速过快，对路况不熟悉，加之由南向北这一路段基本都是下坡路，<Event eid="e19"><Location lid="l19">前方</Location>发生<Denoter type="emergency" did="d19">事故</Denoter></Event>后，
<Event polarity="negative" eid="e20"><Denoter type="action" did="d20">刹车</Denoter>不及</Event>或
<Event eid="e21"><Object sid="s21">刹车</Object><Denoter type="stateChange" did="d21">失灵</Denoter></Event>，
<Event eid="e22">才导致<Denoter type="emergency" did="d22">多起事故</Denoter>发生</Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
  
  <Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e23" type="thoughtevent"><Participant sid="s23">记者</Participant>从<Participant oid="o23">陕西省高速集团</Participant><Denoter type="perception" did="d23">了解</Denoter>到</Event>，
  <Event eid="e24"><Object sid="s24">西安到汉中高速公路</Object>从<Time type="relTime" tid="t24">八日中午</Time>起被迫<Denoter type="operation" did="d24">实行</Denoter><Object oid="24">单幅通行</Object></Event>。</Sentence>
  <Sentence><Event eid="e25">大量从<Location type="origin" lid="l25">汉中</Location><Denoter type="movement" did="d25">前往</Denoter><Location type="destination" lid="l25">西安</Location>的<Object sid="s25,s26">车辆</Object></Event><Event eid="e26"><Denoter type="action" did="d26">滞留</Denoter>于<Location lid="l26">汉中龙亭收费站附近路面上</Location>，持续时间已<Time type="timeInterval" tid="t26">超过三十小时</Time></Event>。</Sentence>(完)</Paragraph>
